  "texts": [
    "RQ4: Vocabulary adaptation helps in high novelty settings.",
    "We observe that vocabulary adaptation improves over BASE in six out of eight high novelty settings.",
    "The average performance improvement (wherever observed) is 11.92% and 18.03% for Llama-2 and Llama-3.1 when com-pared to BASE.",
    "Thus, ScafFix is the best vocabulary adaptation strategy in high novelty settings as it outperformed in five out of eight settings.",
